{"tid":2252273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新城市廣場警長斷指案 作供警坦言僅見被告「含住」遇襲同袍手指","createTime":"2020-10-21T11:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T11:32:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef23be91c01dc09a52b6cf1de0a72bc928adc21","tid":2252273,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:05:18.000Z","msg":"港大畢業生去年7月14日在沙田新城市廣場衝突中，被指咬斷偵緝警長梁啟業的手指。他否認蓄意傷人等罪，案件今日續審。當日有份拘捕被告的便衣警員在辯方盤問下，同意當時僅看到被告「含住咗」梁的手指，加上被告戴著口罩，只見到梁的手指「屈實」在被告口中，看不清被告有否咬實牙關。至於他供稱被告咬梁的手指，只是建基於當時聽到梁大叫「放開」而作出的推斷。<br />\n<br />\n警員23491供稱，當晚他與偵緝警長梁啟業和高級警司梁子健合力制服被告杜啟華（22歲）時，被告激烈掙扎並想逃走，其間他聽到有人大叫「放開」，並看到被告咬住梁啟業的手指。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/MX57TYWYWVEG3JHF3GI7ZXSD7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FMX57TYWYWVEG3JHF3GI7ZXSD7U%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=2474ac37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FMX57TYWYWVEG3JHF3GI7ZXSD7U%2F&h=93a19a0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/MX57TYWYWVEG3JHF3GI7ZXSD7U/</a>"},{"pid":"dff3a9dec096b00a23e5c2aa6db94fbdfa30da00","tid":2252273,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:07:05.000Z","msg":"幅圖做乜鳩?"},{"pid":"c921b26571f04a90b7070cd32deebab6be0b7677","tid":2252273,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff3a9dec096b00a23e5c2aa6db94fbdfa30da00","tid":2252273,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:07:05.000Z","msg":"幅圖做乜鳩?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:08:50.000Z","msg":"唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,手足有開POST可以問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces